President Obama has nominated Judge Lucy Haeran Koh to serve on the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit. Judge Koh has served as a United States District Judge for the Northern District of California since 2010 and previously served as a California Superior Court Judge for Santa Clara County from 2008 to 2010. She has a distinguished legal career and has received several recognitions for her work. Judge Koh has also been involved in various bar and professional organizations throughout her career. President Obama praised her integrity and evenhandedness and looks forward to adding her wisdom and experience to the Ninth Circuit Court.